Subject: [PATCH] btrfs: don't take device_list_mutex when querying zone info
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 6.19.12
Git-commit: 77603ab10429fe713a03345553ca8dbbfb1d91c6

[ Upstream commit 77603ab10429fe713a03345553ca8dbbfb1d91c6 ]

